### Configure Edge Middleware Routes

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/build-output-api/features

Defines routing rules that invoke an Edge Middleware function for matching URLs before passing the request to the underlying resource. Uses the middlewarePath property to specify the middleware and src pattern for URL matching.

```json
{
  "routes": [
    {
      "src": "/api/(.*)",
      "middlewareRawSrc": ["/api"],
      "middlewarePath": "auth",
      "continue": true
    }
  ]
}
```

