### Specify Runtime for Vercel Routing Middleware (Node.js or Edge)

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/llms-full

This `middleware.ts` configuration snippet demonstrates how to explicitly change the execution runtime for Vercel Routing Middleware. By default it's 'edge', but it can be set to 'nodejs' for middleware that requires a Node.js environment.

```javascript
export const config = {
  runtime: 'nodejs', // or 'edge' (default)
