When working with Vercel Edge middleware, especially when modifying `Astro.locals` via `src/vercel-edge-middleware.ts`, installing the `@vercel/functions` package is crucial for TypeScript typing. These commands show how to install the package using various Node.js package managers.

```Bash
pnpm i @vercel/functions
```

```Bash
yarn add @vercel/functions
```

```Bash
